{"title":"危险的组合","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2825","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>有一些装有铀(用U表示)和铅(用L表示)的盒子，数量均足够多。要求把N个盒子放成一行，但至少有3个U放在一起，有多少种方法？</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p><span style=\"\">包含一个整数</span><span style=\"\">N</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Courier New'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Courier New'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">输出一个整数表示方法数。</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>样例1：4</p>\n<p>样例2：5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>样例1：3</p>\n<p>样例2：8</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>对于100%的数据（<span style=\"\">3&lt;=N&lt;=30</span>）</p>\n<p>样例1解释：</p>\n<p>UUUL、LUUU、UUUU</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>样例2解释：</p>\n<p>UUUUL、UUUUU、UUULU、UUULL、LUUUU、LUUUL、ULUUU、LLUUU</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}